XPilot clients often exit on normal quit with an X11 error message:

 X Error of failed request:  BadWindow (invalid Window parameter)
   Major opcode of failed request:  2 (X_ChangeWindowAttributes)
   Resource id in failed request:  0x80012c
   Serial number of failed request:  2600340
   Current serial number in output stream:  2600345

and exit status = 1.  The first 2 lines are always the same,
the last 3 differ (depend on length of game i guess).
My X-Server is XFree86 Version 4.5.0 on NetBSD 3.0.1.

