- In Key Config, the button to change should be drawn
activated (e.g. dark background) after it was clicked
and remain activated until a keypress occurred.
Then it should deactivate and update it's contents.
Otherwise it seems to work. Backspace does clear all
keys for the current function. Maybe that is intended.?
One could add an Undo button to the
"Close | Prev | Next" button row. It would restore
the previous settings for the last changed button,
but only if that is displayed on the current page.
So that the player does not accidentally undo some
wrong function binding.

